{"tid":513982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做gym計算熱量問題","createTime":"2017-12-30T06:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T04:43:55.000Z","uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a6863eab0942b42381ce943b28f228868cdd81","tid":513982,"uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"你地平時係點按計到既熱量黎食野<br />\n咁平時食開家常便飯 茶記 又要點計 <br />\n有冇飲食gym友教學 <br />\n最易睇只係包裝野啲熱量 <br />\n利申：體重過輕"},{"pid":"fd6225f8c69822e8fface033c854e4066403c200","tid":513982,"uid":11876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"增重基本上唔洗計得咁準，就算計到咁準你都好難完全follow晒，外出食飯既熱量亦好難計得咁準<br />\n除左一日三餐，再加兩餐小食（食下d蛋白質，carb) 基本上都work<br />\n但都唔代表你可以亂9咁食，要少食油炸野，多汁，多工序既食物<br />\n真係想計既就要自己google下食物既熱量<br />\nBMR x activity level x ~1.15就大約係你所需既熱量"},{"pid":"838ba2a15e5c32276afe962e201f7edcaf5a5603","tid":513982,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.calculator.net/calorie-calculator.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculator.net%2Fcalorie-calculator.html%3F&d=eMxLSFjhcSOg0%2B67prlU3E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=1a1b2fcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.calculator.net/calorie-calculator.html?</a>"},{"pid":"60394c206d5873eb9f95a9e9baaedae3e3b04434","tid":513982,"uid":134549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05d5e958e82c21854d799804b6feaa340c99da06","tid":513982,"uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>增重基本上唔洗計得咁準，就算計到咁準你都好難完全follow晒，外出食飯既熱量亦好難計得咁準<br />\n除左一日三餐，再加兩餐小食（食下d蛋白質，carb) 基本上都work<br />\n但都唔代表你可以亂9咁食，要少食油炸野，多汁，多工序既食物<br />\n真係想計既就要自己google下食物既熱量<br />\nBMR x activity level x ~1.15就大約係你所需既熱量</blockquote><br />\n我本身有暗瘡問題 所以都戒曬所有唔健康既野 平時冇又乜點買野食 通常都係一日三餐就算數"},{"pid":"2c91308a9988c03107078c18683189f5e1d8a701","tid":513982,"uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.calculator.net/calorie-calculator.html?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.calculator.net%2Fcalorie-calculator.html%3F&d=eMxLSFjhcSOg0%2B67prlU3E%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=1a1b2fcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.calculator.net/calorie-calculator.html?</a></blockquote><br />\n我都有用過呢個 但係唔識點follow"},{"pid":"c24135ca27439b209f13bbdf036f4bfe7727697a","tid":513982,"uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好難計，有用過MyFitnessPal一排。但唔係咩野食database都有。</blockquote><br />\n係啊 所以專業既gym友都幾勁 由其是外國既"},{"pid":"7bc0838673e3913a5c2cf83200d9d210eacafb25","tid":513982,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c24135ca27439b209f13bbdf036f4bfe7727697a","tid":513982,"uid":152230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好難計，有用過MyFitnessPal一排。但唔係咩野食database都有。</blockquote><br />\n係啊 所以專業既gym友都幾勁 由其是外國既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"果啲通常餐餐都自製"},{"pid":"aeb03862fdf527c3de9562083024e69d8d6c664d","tid":513982,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"體重過輕仲計乜鬼熱量，盡量食啲乾淨卡路里同阻力運動啦"}]}